{"tid":527791,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做炒散咁勤力搏乜","createTime":"2018-01-13T05:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T02:28:46.000Z","uid":134626,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9be42aa34566411093c8ed9239aba2b1de89c672","tid":527791,"uid":134626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:14:13.000Z","msg":"話說前日小弟翻酒店炒散 <br />\n本身就無乜野做 人手夠多 <br />\n啲野可以慢慢做<br />\n但係就見到有條仆街 起勢咁做野<br />\n摺餐巾抹銀器執餐快槍手咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實做炒散慢慢做唔可以咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估你做得快會加人工咩 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你!系話梗你啊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a2b5eed46fd4a998fae72b50f8bbc455b3416","tid":527791,"uid":108236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"勤力有女屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b4a8e651d97199d4638d4e5b1196235e170f133","tid":527791,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"多你十蚊"},{"pid":"96f99ba7d6c979f18f7879d53438a96d88d7c5de","tid":527791,"uid":27729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/13/140737_466363d2f118f76a93f163eae91c1cd4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F13%2F140737_466363d2f118f76a93f163eae91c1cd4.png&h=7cee0056&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3bcf7630abba9279d00230af299b0c4b044dc66","tid":527791,"uid":95517,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T06:16:33.000Z","msg